Package: about
Type: Package
Title: Read and Write Metadata
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Matt Johnson
Maintainer: Matt Johnson <mrjoh3@gmail.com>
Description: The purpose of about is to read and write metadata. Specifically it 
    can read the metadata from any webpage and it can write arbitrary metadata to 
    the `YAML` header of an [Rmarkdown](https://rmarkdown.rstudio.com/) or 
    [Quarto](https://quarto.org/) file.
